\nc<>\bustMsgExp[2,1]Finally awake, huh? \.\.\bustMsgExp[2,2] Class is already
over, senpai.

\ncHey, hey, how about we go to the cafe that opened in front
of the station next time? I heard their crepes are amazing~.
\nc<Female Student 2>Really? But if we eat too much, we might gain weight~.
\nc<Female Student 1>Ehh~? Ayachan, you're super thin! If it were me,
\nc<>(I was just feeling drowsy and spaced out...)

\nc<>(I wonder if my gaze has become fierce because I always
glare at villains.)

\nc<>(My job as a magical girl kept me busy and my friends
drifted away.)(And in the process, I completely forgot how
to make friends.)
\nc<>(...I shouldn't have become a magical girl after all...)

\nc<>Can I call you Kei-san? Please take care of me from now
on!
\nc<>(...Maybe I should try a little harder.)

\nc<>(I wonder if I should at least get to know the class
representative.)
\nc<Female Student 1>Ah, Kei-san, you look exceptionally beautiful today.

\ncYou still have that aura that keeps people away, huh?
Seriously, it's a waste with such a face.

\TA[1](...I feel like they're talking bad about me. I should stay
away.)

\TA[1](You're still popular, huh.) (That's why you would talk to
an introverted transfer student like me, right?)

\TA[1](To be honest, I want to be friends rather than just
Senpai.) (But you're the only person who talks to me...)

\TA[1]\BustMsgExp[2,5]Now, I'll let you copy my notes for just one cup of coffee!

\TA[1](We still have a little time until we meet the magical

\TA[1](Alright, if I quickly copy them at the cafe--)
\TA[1](This is a signal that a villain has appeared...!)

\TA[1]Sorry, I have to go! Please take care of the notes for me
next time!
